3 thank you car !	you are welcome my driver !

3 will it be stormy in the next two_days ?	the next two_days will be stormy , one will be stormy with a low of 80f and a high of 90f and the other will be windy , low of 40f with a high of 50f
4 thanks	not a problem

4 thanks	not a problem
